{"tid":2252231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 將發行睽違三年的正規專輯　回歸當晚舉行特別演出！","createTime":"2020-10-21T10:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:27:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f45d4d424b36112e3590caadf4d614d9b44e88","tid":2252231,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"再過不到一週，TWICE 就要帶著正規二輯〈Eyes wide open〉回歸了，當晚就能馬上看到新歌的現場表演！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（21 日）宣布 TWICE 將於 10 月 26 日晚間 8 點（韓國時間），在 YouTube 和 NAVER V LIVE 上同步舉行《TWICE &quot;I CAN'T STOP ME&quot; SPECIAL LIVE》。<br />\n<br />\n當晚 TWICE 除了會表演以 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 為首的多首新專輯收錄曲，也會分享準備久違的正規專輯的故事。特別的是，〈Eyes wide open〉不僅有朴軫永、Heize 和 Dua Lipa 等音樂人參與創作，志效、Sana、多賢、彩瑛和娜璉也分別貢獻了歌詞，攜手打造富有 TWICE 色彩的 13 首歌。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 將於 26 日傍晚 6 點正式發行〈Eyes wide open〉，不過成員定延日前因心理方面的問題而必須休養，這次並不會參加活動。希望她能早日康復！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0a8b31a7d78b61f15ae73b0cc38e396e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-21/131043-881135.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0a8b31a7d78b61f15ae73b0cc38e396e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-21%2F131043-881135.jpeg&h=1d7ad479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"83da13b401ed98ee9d3d26e669a870796309af63","tid":2252231,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"牙隱寫咗咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb1ff43472a3d12ab66ea2948cda7d11dcb36b9","tid":2252231,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"83da13b401ed98ee9d3d26e669a870796309af63","tid":2252231,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"牙隱寫咗咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"同我既愛歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"